      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "--APIS:--\nList chats \nGET /v1/chats: \nspecific conversation path:\nGET /v1/chats/{chatid}/messages?branchid=abc\nDELETE /v1/chats/{chatid}\n\nws /v1/stream:\n\nclient -> server ; { chatid, prompt, parentid}\nserver -> client; { type: \"token\", data: \"hello\", messageid: \"...\" }",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
